n)\\n  - 材质/工艺/质感说明 (material/craft/texture descriptions)\\n  - 纹样/色彩/寓意说明 (pattern/color/symbolism explanations)\\n  - 穿着顺序/构成流程 (wearing sequence/construction flow)\\n  - 核心特征总结 (core feature summary)\\nConstraints: must preserve all layout zones as specified, must use Simplified Chinese exclusively, must achieve \\\"真实写实主视觉、结构拆解、中文标注、材质说明、纹样寓意、色彩含义和核心特征总结\\\" (realistic main visual, structural breakdown, Chinese annotations, material descriptions, pattern symbolism, color meanings, core feature summary), must avoid poster/photography studio/e-commerce/anime/cosplay aesthetics\\nAvoid: must avoid poster feeling, photography studio feeling, e-commerce feeling, anime feeling, cosplay feeling, incorrect annotations, wrong structures, illegible text, fake materials, excessive decoration\", \"size\": \"1536x1024\", \"quality\": \"medium\", \"n\": 1, \"output_format\": \"png\"}",
